    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi Clementvp, you need to declare the attributes for faceting in the dashboard OR use the REST settings call to set them from a script for instance that would run on your infrastructure: https://www.algolia.com/doc/rest#change-index-settings\n\nThe JS client has a setSettings method: https://github.com/algolia/algoliasearch-client-js#index-settings\n\nThen once the attributes for faceting are defined in your settings, you can use any refinementList or menu or hierarchicalMenu widget.\n\nLet me know how it goes.\n",
