    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Ok good form me with the REST API.\n\nBut when i try with the JS client and the setSettings method, like that:\n\nvar client = algoliasearch('APPID', 'APPKEY');\nvar index = client.initIndex('Agoarts');\nindex.setSettings({attributesForFaceting: ['coloris', 'dimension', 'prixttc']});\n\nConsole give me:  AlgoliaSearchError: This method is only available in HTTPS. Why ? \n( my tests are in local).\n\nThank you for your reactivity. \n",
