  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@clementvp when you run a JS script with the JS client we default to the page protocol for all calls. This is something we can fix for all writes to the API since they need to be done in https.\n\nYou can either run this script in node.js OR do this:\n\n``` js\nvar client = algoliasearch('APPID', 'APPKEY', {protocol: 'https:'});\n```\n\nThanks\n",
